summary: Marvel is giving little girls and women the most amazing female characters
title: Marvel is giving little girls and women the most amazing female characters
body:
Like no matter black or white (i sound like Michael Jackson) You can’t deny you have the most amazing examples for little girls and hell, even for women, to look up to. 

Like they learn their lesson with Natasha and she is now a strong independent woman that is able to look at the government and not give a damn about what they can say or do to you.

Wanda Maximoff, someone who has been trought hell losing her brother and now her lover and she has been always fighting

Okoye, literally the most bad ass warrior of Wakanda. Like do i have to say more? “Will you kill me, my love?” “For Wakanda? Always”

Shuri. Like can you imagine little black girls looking up to Shuri and thinking i want to be the most inteligent and amazing scientist the world have met? Like give me more black genius scientist.

MJ? Like it was the first time i heard a black person telling the truth in a marvel movie about Slaves, and literally America’s Story. 

And literally, the list can go forever

And i think one of the things i’m loving the most about marvel is that. Plus the Holly Warrior Trinity “Natasha, Wanda and Okoye”

summary: OK this is a hella long shot but...reaching out to my trek followers for help  The Sci-Fi convention I’m running will only be...
body:
OK this is a hella long shot but…reaching out to my trek followers for help 

The Sci-Fi convention I’m running will only be able to work if the venue is funded but people seem to be holding back as the donations are low…if I can’t secure the venue I’ll have to cancel everything I worked for :(

There’s rewards for every tier, so you don’t actually have to go if you live in the US. Read through them and let me know!

This is the link to the information

You get to have personal coffee with celebrities too :D

If it doesn’t get funded by 9th July then everyone is automatically refunded anyway.

I know we’re all just strangers here but little old me is kinda relying on you guys…I’m not getting as much help as I thought I would 😂

Thank you to anyone that puts their trust in me. Seriously, message me so I can thank you properly and give you your reward. ❤️

summary: I have suddenly developed an obsession with the Avengers. It came out of nowhere. I don’t know why. I was sitting there one...
body: I have suddenly developed an obsession with the Avengers. It came out of nowhere. I don’t know why. I was sitting there one evening minding my own business, wondering what I would watch on Netflix while I ate my dinner, when I suddenly felt I absolutely had to watch Captain America, which honestly is something I never, ever imagined I would take an interest in, like it’s so far out of my range of interests that I just have no idea where it came from or why I’m gripped like this. I’ve been watching those films for years; I mean, I’d go see them once when they first came out, and I enjoyed them but forgot them mere hours after I watched them. Now all of a sudden they have a stranglehold on my imagination. I can’t even pick a favourite Avenger; I’m entranced by them all. I’ll be collecting bloody comic books next.

title: The Avengers go back
body:
Bruce: So when we go back in time, we will know what is going to happen, but all the ones who turned to dust will not.

Shuri: That’s right. And it is VERY IMPORTANT that no-one says anything to the others that might change the way they act and ruin the plan. Everyone has to do exactly what they did before, with just these three changes. Got it?

Tony: Act natural. Got it.

Thor: I always act natural.

Steve: We’re not idiots you know.

*********

Steve: Bucky! It’s….it’s you!

Bucky: Of course it’s me. We were just talking a minute ago. Why are you staring at me like that? Why are you holding my hand? There’s a battle going on here, Steve. This isn’t the time.

Steve: Oh, yes, I know. Just… stick with me, ok?

Bucky: OK. Please let go of my hand so I can fire this gun now.

Steve: Oh, sorry.

*********

Okoye: T’Challa!

M’Baku: My King! 

T’Challa: What’s happened? Is something wrong? M’Baku, why are you crying?

Okoye: *Nudging M’Baku in the ribs* Stop crying you idiot.

M’Baku: No….reason. Some…..dust in my eye. It is so wonderful to see you, T’Challa.

T’Challa: You see me all the time.

Okoye: And it is always wonderful *smiles*.

T’Challa: You two are acting most strangely.

*********

Thor: Groot!

Rocket: Groot! My little seedling, my…. *buries his face in Groot’s branches*

Groot: ………I am Groot?

Thor: We just… thought something had happened to you. But it hasn’t. So we are just…… acting natural.

Groot: I am Groot?

Thor: This is us acting natural.

Rocket: I’m not crying. It’s just….. hay fever.

*********

Tony: Peter! Peter my son!

Peter: I’m….what did you just call me?

Tony: Um, nothing. Just let me hold you *crushes Peter in a hug*.

Peter: Dr Strange, what’s wrong with him?

Stephen: *Smiling* He’s a very odd man, Peter. Just humour him.

***********

Tony: Stephen, I……..

Stephen: I saw the future Tony. You don’t have to explain it to me.

Tony: Oh. I….did you see……

Stephen: That bit where you kept sobbing and repeating my name over and over again?

Tony:

Stephen: Yes I did. Now let’s just get on with the plan.

summary:
y'all: just accept it. Loki is dead. 
me, an intellectual: the mcu still has to make money and I know there's no way they would...
body:
y'all: just accept it. Loki is dead.

me, an intellectual: the mcu still has to make money and I know there’s no way they would just kill T'challa and Peter Parker for example, especially without them at least having two movies. So obviously they’re going to have to somehow get the infinity stones back from Thanos and turn back time in order to bring these characters back to life, and if they go back in time this could also mean going back before Loki dies. …so no, I won’t be accepting his death!
